title: ‘Selling the OC’ Episodes 5-8 | It Was All A Stream
description:
Juliet and Jodi reconvene to discuss the back half of the debut season of this spectacular ‘Selling Sunset’ spinoff, including the absurd drama concerning Kayla’s over-the-line flirting with Tyler, Alex Hall’s dark turn, what the Alexandras have done to piss everybody off, and, of course, the incredibly sloppy yacht trip finale.
Hosts: Juliet Litman and Jodi Walker
Producer: Sasha Ashall
Additional Production: Chelsea Stark-Jones
